Flutter Material Design Icons Gallery

It can be difficult to get an overview of all the Flutter Material Design icons available through the official page as they are desplayed in a single column. This collects them into a gallary view, and allows similar icons to be filtered out. To use include the code like this: IconData(0xee29, fontFamily: 'MaterialIcons')
